quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,208,"Soni Uwwe nganituujonanjeje musi uliose ikaŵeje wakolaga akutetela."
  26,209,"Kuŵa chikumbusyo, soni Uwwe nganituŵa ŵalupuso (pakwajonanga ŵandu nkanitwatetele)."
  26,210,"Soni mashetani ngaŵa ni gagatulwisye jalakwe (Qur’aniji mwaakuŵechetela achimakafili)."
  33,61,"(Ŵanganyao) ŵalaniwe, palipose paasimanikwe akwembekanyisidwe ni awulajidwe kwanneso."
  33,62,"(Aji ni) nyendele ja Allah pa aŵala ŵaŵapite kala, ni ngankusimana kupitikuka kulikose pa nyendele ja Allah."
  33,63,"Ŵandu akum’buusya (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ya ndema (jakwichila Kiyama)? Jilani: “Chisimu umanyilisi wakwe uli kwa Allah pe.” Ana ni chichi chikummanyisya kuti mwine ndemajo kuŵa nkuŵa pakuŵandika?"
  34,40,"Soni (kumbuchilani) lisiku lyatachasonganganya ŵanaose, kaneka ni tachiŵecheta kwa Achimalaika kuti: “Ana ŵanganyaŵa ŵaliji nkun’galagatila jenumanja?”"
  34,41,"Ŵanganyao tachiti: “Kuswejela ni Kwenu! Mmwe ni Nsyoŵe jwetu ngaŵa ŵanganyao. (Ngwamba), nambo ŵaliji nkugagalagatila majini, ŵajinji ŵao ŵaliji nkugakulupilila galakwego.”"
  34,42,"Basi lelo ngaakola jwine mwa jenumanja chikamuchisyo chakunkamuchisya jwine namuno masausyo gakunsausya jwine. Ni tuchiti ku aŵala ŵaŵalitesile lupuso: “Pasyani ilagasyo ya Moto wamwaliji nkuwukaanila.”"
  35,25,"Sano naga achinkanilaga (ngaiŵa yakusimosya), basi pamasile paŵaakaaniile aŵala ŵaŵaliji paujo pao, ŵayichilile achimitenga ŵao ni (ilosyo) yakuonechela palangulangu, ikalakala kwisa soni chitabu chakupeleka lilanguka."
  35,26,"Kaneka nakwembekenye aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu, nambi kwaliji uli kasilika Kwangu (ngati najonasile wosope)?"
  35,27,"Ana nganinyyiona yanti Allah atulwisye kuumila kwinani mesi (gawula), basi ni tukopochesye isogosi yakulekangana mitundu jakwe, nambo soni m’matumbi mwana tumisela tweswela ni twechejeu twakulekangana mitundu jakwe, ni twine twepiliu nnope?"
  36,10,"Soni yalumope kwa jamanjao mwatetele kapena nkatetela, ngaakulupililape."
  36,11,"Chisimu mmwe mpaka muntetele (ni kunkamuchisya kutetelako) ajula jwaakukuya chikumbusyo (Qur’an), ni kun’jogopaga (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji mwangali kum’bona, basi munsengwasyani ya (kupata) chikululuko kwisa soni malipilo gakuchimbichika."
  36,12,"Chisimu Uwwe ni ŵatuchijimusya ŵawe, ni tukulembaga yaŵalongwesye (kupanganya ni katika malipilo gakwe), ni sajo syao (syaŵaliji nkwenda kuja kutenda ibada, ni masengo gaŵapanganyisye gagakwendelechela malipilo gakwe), sano chindu chilichose tuchisunjile (pakuchilemba) m’chitabu chakusalichisya (chilichose Al-Lauh Al-Mahfȗz)."